strings:
<voice_0x01001193><se_def>*: What happened!?
What are you two doing together!?

<voice_0x01001194><se_def>*: Does this mean ya still don't know
who won?

<voice_0x01001195><se_high>*: Come on, it's obvious.
It must have been a draw.
<voice_0x01001196><se_low>*: Does this mean the casino's gonna stay closed? Gimme a break!

<voice_0x01001197><se_def>Cash: Listen up, all of you!
As you can see, the contest was a draw!
However, an heir has been decided!
<voice_0x01001198><se_high>Carrie: Both of us are inheriting our father's fortune. Together.
<voice_0x01001199><se_def>Cash: And as proof, we have both obtained the mark of the Golding clan from the Dragon Graveyard!
<voice_0x0100119A><se_low>*: They look just like the scars Golding had on his hands!
<voice_0x0100119B><se_def>*: Yeah. He used to show 'em off all the time, down the pub, 'e did.

<voice_0x0100119C><se_high>Carrie: We also have some good news for everyone.
The casino will reopen tomorrow!

<voice_0x0100119F><se_def>Cash: And finally, we need to thank you for protecting us, my travelling friends.
But we're exhausted at the moment.

<voice_0x010011A0><se_def>Cash: We'd like you to stay in the mansion tonight
as our guests so we can properly reward you tomorrow.
